{"tid":1537022,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"邊有可能訓得著","createTime":"2019-09-03T19:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T19:41:57.000Z","uid":274369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"94ff64a67745013fed60cd829ffbe1bededdc6a0","tid":1537022,"uid":274369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:02:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔可以慣呀香港人！記住每個手足所承受既暴力同屈辱！"},{"pid":"f3c84b0cd41de970bbce1ae9da4223eb41f408ff","tid":1537022,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:02:47.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"388a4cdddbde48beb5b69db33dcfd575ba591319","tid":1537022,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94ff64a67745013fed60cd829ffbe1bededdc6a0","tid":1537022,"uid":274369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:02:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔可以慣呀香港人！記住每個手足所承受既暴力同屈辱！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:03:13.000Z","msg":"頂住 有我陪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f568f9f5a7ebddf6533a4398a520bbc1ea6341","tid":1537022,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:06:17.000Z","msg":"有關破壞<br />\n<br />\n公物都只係用公帑，叫工人整。圍差館除左送頭冇乜用。<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好學惡霸美國，搞阻礙香港民主進程官員嘅財產！<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好破壞私物！特別係某啲人嘅私物，財產，公司，物業。<br />\n<br />\n特別係唔犯法嘅情況令啲嘢貶值，例如唔小心跌左啲好臭嘅嘢，識郁嘅嘢啊。黑材料，桃色糾紛乜乜乜啊。<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好！<br />\n<br />\n特別係唔好hit and run! 好衰！"},{"pid":"8f606996987cb0fbf1b1503fbdfad1f2de09136f","tid":1537022,"uid":282798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:08:52.000Z","msg":"唉做隻豬真係簡單好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每日望住手足受傷被捕真係好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c519806c193b524eacdbde7e64742a0291c974","tid":1537022,"uid":229966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:14:38.000Z","msg":"屌真係訓唔到"},{"pid":"33812489a975342585a199431f9f468d1c590612","tid":1537022,"uid":97330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:15:32.000Z","msg":"閃電勇武係唔洗代價架！<br />\n而且少人就成事，大家諗下一個廢老咁慢手腳都可以清晒連儂牆<br />\n對家打埋啲陰陰濕濕既招，我地都可以陰陰濕濕快閃一啲有價值既地方<br />\n十八區都有既時候 啲狗跑得去邊？ 2個人一個地方 36個人都夠<br />\n<br />\n重點：非狗屋 五分鐘快閃 (五分鐘就走邊有人當場拉到? 快閃既定義本身就係咁)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都訓唔著，所以係咁推ＰＯＳＴ"},{"pid":"5fc04a5d5cacdf33464c90b524437fd23820ae80","tid":1537022,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:16:22.000Z","msg":"瞓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded38e00d80af935aac48b42e4e68ba3d98d0e76","tid":1537022,"uid":200021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:16:58.000Z","msg":"明明今日好攰但又真係瞓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好嬲好心痛 唔知做咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ba32a6670f9851c64b28f46168931c5b8809fd","tid":1537022,"uid":163167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:30:27.000Z","msg":"記住呢份傷痛同憤怒<br />\n終有一日<br />\n我地會一次過還返哂比佢地<br />\n<br />\n我地仲有長期作戰<br />\n各位手足保重呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161a3088828f63dd5ef83dfb8f123f9f4fba7388","tid":1537022,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:34:17.000Z","msg":"要繼續戰鬥落去!<br />\n咁多位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一齊加油!"},{"pid":"500ce628d77d7ba6a6b2769561e39d1363966c85","tid":1537022,"uid":282494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94ff64a67745013fed60cd829ffbe1bededdc6a0","tid":1537022,"uid":274369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:02:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔可以慣呀香港人！記住每個手足所承受既暴力同屈辱！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:41:57.000Z","msg":"習慣了便成為奴隸<br />\n成為了奴隸也不知已是奴隸"}]}